object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT 
metal_acl.source_name,
metal_acl.load_type,
metal_acl.id,
metal_acl.agency_nup,
metal_acl.field_name,
metal_acl.before_value,
metal_acl.after_value,
metal_acl.unique_id,
metal_acl."type",
metal_acl.guidewire_id,
metal_acl.page,
metal_acl.created,
metal_acl.modified,
tgt.adm_agency_change_log_row_id,
tgt.adm_agency_change_log_batch_id,
tgt.adm_agency_change_log_md5checksum,
tgt.adm_agency_change_log_row_effective_end_datetime,
tgt.id as tgt_id,
tgt.agency_nup as tgt_agency_nup,
tgt.field_name as tgt_field_name,
tgt.page as tgt_page,
tgt.created as tgt_created,
current_batch.batch_id
FROM $$raw_schema.adm_agency_change_log metal_acl
LEFT JOIN $$staging_schema.adm_agency_change_log tgt
ON metal_acl.id = tgt.id 
AND tgt.adm_agency_change_log_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
LEFT JOIN current_batch
ON TRUE
